波尔多市区内共有6个派出所<ref group="社">{{Cite web|url=https://demarchesadministratives.fr/commissariat-police/bordeaux-33000|title=COMMISSARIAT DE POLICE À BORDEAUX 33000|accessdate=2019-09-01|author=demarchesadministratives.fr|language=fr|publisher=demarchesadministratives.fr|archive-date=2021-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211101051803/https://demarchesadministratives.fr/commissariat-police/bordeaux-33000|dead-url=no}}</ref>、1个国家宪兵队<ref group="社">{{Cite web|url=https://demarchesadministratives.fr/gendarmerie/bordeaux-33000|title=GENDARMERIE À BORDEAUX 33000|accessdate=2019-08-01|author=demarchesadministratives.fr|language=fr|publisher=demarchesadministratives.fr|archive-date=2021-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816180024/https://demarchesadministratives.fr/gendarmerie/bordeaux-33000|dead-url=no}}</ref>和1个消防站<ref group="社">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bordeaux.fr/l4075/caserne-des-sapeurs-pompiers-ornano|title=CASERNE DES SAPEURS-POMPIERS ORNANO|accessdate=2019-09-01|author=bordeaux.fr|language=fr|publisher=bordeaux.fr|archive-date=2021-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211101060730/https://www.bordeaux.fr/l4075/caserne-des-sapeurs-pompiers-ornano|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

